At E-Lien, the privacy and protection of your personal and information is very important to us. That's why we've created this privacy statement, which fully describes our information gathering and dissemination practices. It is the best way we can demonstrate our firm commitment to your privacy. E-Lien uses the data you enter into our database for the following purposes:
<br>
<ul>
